
'''海伦娜·克罗宁'''（{{lang-en|Helena Cronin}}，{{bd|1942年|}}）是一位英国[[達爾文主義|達爾文主義]][[哲學家|哲學家]]家和[[理性主义|理性主义]]者，[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]]教授<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/1999/aug/28/1 |title=Darwin's darling |author=Anne Perkins <!-- so it appears from a non-traditional byline --> |date=28 August 1999 |website=www.theguardian.com |publisher=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate=29 December 2017 |archive-date=2017-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230060336/https://www.theguardian.com/science/1999/aug/28/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主要科普作品有《蚂蚁与孔雀：耀眼羽毛背后的性选择之争》（''The Ant and the Peacock: Altruism and Sexual Selection from Darwin to Today''）等。
